  <thing id="cWHMock" name="Mock" description="The witch can deride the  prowess and effectiveness of a creature within 60 feet of her, causing it to become clumsy and self-conscious. The target is \nstaggered for a number of rounds equal to the witch&#146;s level. A Will save negates this effect. If the target fails the saving throw, it can attempt to make a new save each round to end the effect. Whether or not the saving throw is successful, a creature cannot be the target of this hex again for 1 day. This is a\nmind-affecting, language-dependent effect." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="unique">
