  <thing id="cWHRestore" name="Restoration" description="By invoking mysterious entities, the witch can undo some of the most serious diseases and ailments a character can suffer. The witch can grant  restoration to a target by touching it. \n\nThis acts as a {i}lesser restoration{/i}, {i}neutralize poison{/i}, or {i}remove disease{/i} spell, as determined by the witch when the hex is used. \n\nAt 15th level this spell acts as a {i}heal{/i} spell, except it does not restore any hit points and does not act like harm against undead creatures. \n\nOnce a creature has benefitted from the restoration hex, it cannot benefit from it again for 24 hours." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="unique">
