  <thing id="fWHQuikHex" name="Quicken Hex" description="You can use a hex quickly.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Int 13, major hex class feature.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: Once per day you can use a hex ( but not a major hex) as a swift action. At 18th level you can use a major hex (but not a grand hex) as a swift action.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: You can select this feat more than once. Each time you select this feat, you can use this ability an additional time per day." compset="Feat" summary="You can use a hex quickly.">
